<br />
1----SoE made a mistake on mobs' level (Or just laziness and forgot about DC and mobs shouldn't summon at lvl 45)
<br />
2----May be they make a mistake and tagged the mob's ability to summon(another very easy mistake)
<br />
3----May be they forgot to tag the mobs uncharmable (it has happenned many times before)
<br />
4----It is SoE's intend to give a chanter a DC pet that hits for 300+ and summons. (i highly doubt it). 
